The `check` execution is misconfigured.

Configuration contains list of rule with element type and list of limits. So `&lt;element&gt;` tag belongs to `&lt;rule&gt;` not to `&lt;limits&gt;`

Use this snippet

```xml
&lt;configuration&gt;
    &lt;rules&gt;
        &lt;rule&gt;
            &lt;element&gt;CLASS&lt;/element&gt;
            &lt;limits&gt;
                &lt;limit&gt;
                    &lt;counter&gt;INSTRUCTION&lt;/counter&gt;
                    &lt;value&gt;COVEREDRATIO&lt;/value&gt;
                    &lt;minimum&gt;0.90&lt;/minimum&gt;
                &lt;/limit&gt;
            &lt;/limits&gt;
        &lt;/rule&gt;
    &lt;/rules&gt;
&lt;/configuration&gt;
```

