        @JsonInclude(JsonInclude.Include.NON_NULL)

Basically if you can conditionally set a value to null, you can then exclude it entirely from serialization using the above annotation. Here&#39;s a quick example.

    @JsonInclude(JsonInclude.Include.NON_NULL)
